# 6. Probability & Expectation Proof Mechanics

## Expectation Arguments

| Tool | Use |
|---|---|
| Linearity | Decompose sums |
| Conditioning | Simplify dependence |
| Total expectation | Eliminate hidden vars |

---

## Almost Sure / High-Probability Proofs

| Pattern |
|---|
| Prove event holds outside null set |
| Or bound failure probability |

**Failure mode:** confusing expectation bounds with probability bounds.

